<div style="font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: auto;">
  <h2 style="color: #6366f1;">Match Found!</h2>
  <p>Hello,</p>
  <p>Great news! Our matching engine has located a potential match for the document reported in your case.</p>
  <div style="background: #fdf2f2; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 25px 0; border: 1px solid #fee2e2;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #991b1b;">Match Summary</h3>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Match ID:</strong> {{match.matchNumber}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Document Type:</strong> {{match.lostDocumentCase.case.document.type.name}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Lost Case:</strong> #{{match.lostDocumentCase.case.caseNumber}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Found Case:</strong> #{{match.foundDocumentCase.case.caseNumber}}</p>
  </div>
  <p>You can view the full details of this match and proceed with verification here:</p>
  <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="https://citizenlink.app/matches/{{match.id}}" style="background-color: #6366f1; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">View Match Details</a>
  </div>
  <p>Thank you for using Citizen Link to help reunite lost documents with their owners.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br><strong>Citizen Link Team</strong></p>
  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 40px;" />
  <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #999;">If the button does not work, copy and paste this link: https://citizenlink.app/matches/{{match.id}}</p>
</div>